259
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:15,320
Let’s go. Come on.

260
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,550
Jump together on my count.

261
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,960
One, two, three.

262
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,750
