264
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:38,150
Darling, I’m sorry.

265
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,440
I shouldn’t have brought Heng to peek

266
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:42,200
at the Xie’s Mansion.

267
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,120
I’ll deal with you

268
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:49,630
once I get Heng out.

269
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:53,960
Darling. I won’t get up

270
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,750
until you forgive me.

271
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:01,790
I know I made a mistake.

272
00:15:01,790 --> 00:15:04,870
I shouldn’t have acted on my own,

273
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:05,840
darling.

274
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:11,600
Kneel

275
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,440
all you want.

276
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,670
Darling! Darling!

277
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:28,870
I’m in serious trouble!

278
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,270
